                        We provide ambulance services to take you in our clinic in emergency situation.
                        Just call us, we will arrive in your location.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="box">
                    <h3><i class="fas fa-procedures"></i>Emergency Service</h3>
                    <p>
                        We always provide you service when needed. Feel free to come to our
                        clinic in emergency situation.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="box">
                    <h3><i class="fas fa-stethoscope"></i> Free Check ups</h3>
                    <p>
                        We provides a free check up on the <b>31<sup>st</sup> December</b> of every year.
                        Don't miss the opportunity and check up your whole body for free.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-md-6 d-none d-md-block">
                <img src="~/fonts/img/About.svg" width="100%" alt="">
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
